# Description: Resource waste – assigning crew to unused boats.
# Scenario: Two boats, one person (P1), and task A1 (5h) requires no qualifications.
# Reasoning: P1 may be assigned to any boat without affecting WorkHours, since A1 does not require personnel.
# This makes such assignments irrelevant for the objective function and therefore not meaningful.
# Additional note: The model does not include a passenger capacity constraint for boats.
# As a result, crew distribution across boats does not influence feasibility or objective value unless explicitly linked to tasks.
# Expected result: WorkHours = 5 (task executed). Crew assignment is arbitrary and does not affect the outcome.
# Maximize WorkHours: 5.
data;
set TASKS := A1;
set QUALIS := Tech;
set PEOPLE := P1 P2 P3;
set TOOLS := W1;

param amountBoats := 1;
param maxWorkingHours := 10;

param duration := A1 5;

param hasQuali := P1 Tech 1 P2 Tech 1 P3 Tech 1;
param requiredQualis := A1 Tech 1;
param requiredTools := A1 W1 0;
param stockTools := W1 0;

# Wir können hier kein Bootslimit testen, da es den Parameter im Modell nicht gibt.
end;
